 沒有終點　永沒有終點　那永遠極遠"},{"pid":"b1e411914bfdc8dcca170ecd74a34a5d35968925","tid":733820,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tkCcf5ZDqAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtkCcf5ZDqAo&d=%2BDHbO%2FzWHDxt69RyF4bxTG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e2878849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tkCcf5ZDqAo</a>"},{"pid":"ff71860cd2b31f7a390b1c6219c33f144c695a4f","tid":733820,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"如果雨之後"},{"pid":"1f38b9690277595b6d2362917b82647f4df2f476","tid":733820,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"蘇打綠 我好想你<br />\n<br />\n于文文 體面<br />\n<br />\nDear Jane 最後一次"},{"pid":"00013553f1cd598bf3eab7d99688b3dc90bdb271","tid":733820,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f38b9690277595b6d2362917b82647f4df2f476","tid":733820,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"蘇打綠 我好想你<br />\n<br />\n于文文 體面<br />\n<br />\nDear Jane 最後一次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"聽過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}